      "narrator_chain": {
        "parts": [
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": "٣١٨. وَقِيلَ لَهُ (عليه ‏السلام): بِأَيِّ شَيْ‏ءٍ غَلَبْتَ الْأَقْرَانَ، فَقَالَ"
          }
        ]
      },
      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/nahj-al-balagha:3:201:1",
      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/32/3/318/392",
      "text": [
        " (عليه السلام): مَا لَقِيتُ رَجُلًا إِلَّا أَعَانَنِى عَلَى نَفْسِهِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
          "318. Amīr al-mu’minīn, peace be upon him, was asked: With what did you overpower your adversaries? He answered: Whenever I confronted a person he helped me against himself."
        ]
      }
    },
